I"|<h2 id="setting-the-stage">Setting the Stage</h2>

<p>So, companies use a bunch of tools.</p>

<p>Sometimes the tools talk to each other, sometimes they don’t.</p>

<p>When the tools talk to each other, it isn’t always clear what is next.</p>

<p>However, once the next steps are clear, say make a visual of the relationship, it still lacks the “so what?” component.</p>

